{"tid":1953551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍晉三：疫情下日本處於戰後未經歷過之國難狀況","createTime":"2020-04-01T08:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:04:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5a06a32f8439181b946a34279f7b9d66543b9172","tid":1953551,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1518216_1_L_20200401161018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1518216_1_L_20200401161018.jpg&h=796482cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三在國會參議院一個委員會上，交代政府抗擊新型冠狀病毒疫情的工作。被問到一旦東京的確診個案激增，當局如何應對，安倍強調要設想最壞情況，正就各種可能性做準備。<br />\n<br />\n安倍形容，日本在疫情之下，目前處於戰後從未經歷過的「國難」狀況，政府將於下星期商討緊急經濟對策。他又說東京奧運會及殘奧會延期一年，正探討能否將原本安排給警備人員的宿舍，用作醫療用途。<br />\n<br />\n至於會否「封城」，安倍說政府會就疫情發展，提出各項要求，但日本與法國等歐洲國家情況不同，無法做到「封城」，相關法律的強制力亦較弱。"},{"pid":"981dfbfacf0e929c538e9c0c7529b5c7046b3b04","tid":1953551,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"311<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcce5368e145ab693f5e25ba47c6bf075cd3266a","tid":1953551,"uid":61030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"佢個罩帶得咁撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a9ccc3ccd1173ac9c0d26d9740dbf12fd0b0b9","tid":1953551,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"安倍：最緊要有得奶共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/11/11/world/11chinajapan1/11chinajapan1-master1050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2014%2F11%2F11%2Fworld%2F11chinajapan1%2F11chinajapan1-master1050.jpg&h=a414921c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2980194/org/35c2ec6e0a753f2eb2bd9b2ca7178a3e.JPG/c23r_aeUgVLBiohZrozVHviUOR6